Package: subnetSearch
Version: VERSION
Architecture: amd64
Maintainer: greshnik200ready2die <thriilerchiller123@gmail.com>
Homepage: https://github.com/greshnik200ready2die/SubnetSearch
Description: IP address and subnet classification tool
 SubnetSearch classifies IP addresses, domains and CIDR ranges to identify
 hosting providers, geolocation, reputation, and network diagnostics.
 .
 Features: hosting detection, ASN lookup, geolocation, ping, traceroute,
 port scanning, provider scanning via RIPE Stat and PeeringDB.
Depends: traceroute, iputils-ping, ca-certificates
